description: Barcode Professional for Windows Phone generates high quality vector-based Linear, Composite and 2D Symbologies. Features: - Linear & 2D Barcodes - data-binding support, raster image exportation (WriteableBitmap), Barcode rotation (0, 90, 180, 270 degrees), Full design-time support Visual Studio 2010, Visual Studio Express Editions (Visual Basic, Visual C#), Expression Blend . Supported Barcode Symbologies - USS Code 128 A-B-C, USS Code 39, USS Code 93, Data Matrix ECC200, EAN-13, GTIN-13, EAN-8, GTIN-8, EAN-99, Coupon Barcode, EAN-Velocity, Industrial 2 of 5, Standard 2 of 5, Interleaved 2 of 5, ITF 25, ISBN, Bookland EAN, ISBN-13, ISBN-10, ISMN, ISSN, ITF-14, EAN-14, DUN-14, GTIN-14, JAN-13, JAN-8, PDF417, Portable Data File 417, PDF417 Truncated, SCC-14, SSCC-18, UPC-128, EAN-18, UCC-EAN-128, EAN-128, GTIN-128, UPC-A, UPC-E, GTIN-12, QR Code, Semacode, Aztec Code, Compact PDF417, Macro PDF417, Micro PDF417, Micro QR Code, UPS MaxiCode, GS1 DataBar, RSS-14, Matrix 2 of 5, GS1 DataMatrix, ALL EAN.UCC Composite Barcodes CC-A, CC-B, CC-C
releaseNotes:
# Fixed! A bug in the Auto encoding algorithm for Data Matrix 2D symbology

summary: Add advanced barcodes to Windows Phone Silverlight apps. It supports Linear (1D) and 2D Symbologies.
title: Windows Phone Barcode Pro
